unittitle_ssm: Brooklyn Historical Society Genealogical vertical files
abstract_ssm: This collection was compiled by Brooklyn Historical Society staff to organize their genealogical research and the research of other professional and amateur genealogists. The collection includes correspondence, newspaper clippings, notes, pedigree charts, and a limited number of photographs.
